{"tid":838521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超蓮巴黎晒長腿：隨便拍都好看","createTime":"2018-09-27T07:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T16:52:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":32,"dislike":472,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"7341426946a2f4a78031330f100588d88de0a6dc","tid":838521,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"近日獲邀出席巴黎時裝周嘅賭王何鴻燊三房千金何超蓮，連日嚟都喺社交網分享咗唔少靚相。相信睇咗咁多Fashion show嘅超蓮，都增添咗唔少着衫嘅靈感，今日佢又喺網上分享喺街頭擺出chok甫相，見超蓮着上露膊衫配上一頭曲髮，大晒白滑長腿，甚有時尚感，佢仲話：「巴黎就是隨便拍都好看。」另外，仲見佢食法式田螺相，似乎佢呢個旅程正到爆呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/photo/bkn-20180926210008537-0926_00862_001_01b.jpg?20180926210405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180926210008537-0926_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20180926210405&h=120724b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/photo/bkn-20180926210008537-0926_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180926210405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180926210008537-0926_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180926210405&h=4a198d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/photo/bkn-20180926210008537-0926_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180926210405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180926210008537-0926_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180926210405&h=cb3ce8ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0723ea73c3ec0bcc9c35b5c5eea5349098b2a785","tid":838521,"uid":25659,"like":476,"dislike":6,"score":470,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"已劣化"},{"pid":"1f703ff415c987a870ac9b7623de2c6af4d3947b","tid":838521,"uid":205254,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass